data.description: Welcome to the COUNTRY!! Located in the LORANGER SCHOOL DISTRICT, This beautiful home is nestled atop one of the many rolling hills in the established Bella Casa neighborhood. Featuring 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, this semi-open floorpan packs ample space while maintaining it's cozy, southern charm. The kitchen boasts with custom cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless appliances. The primary suite offers his/her closets/sinks, and a separate tub/shower. Relax on the patio and enjoy the peaceful, private, and spacious backyard. Gas fireplace. 2 car garage. Crown moulding throughout, and MORE! Schedule your showing today!
